      <title>德意志银行和工会同意提高邮政银行员工的工资</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-union-agree-raise-pay-postbank-employees-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行管理层周四表示，德意志银行管理层已与工会就其邮政银行部门数千名员工达成了薪资协议，结束了数月的争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-union-agree-raise-pay-postbank-employees-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
